  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd. \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0baf\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1!",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Jaffna. Rescue of an elderly woman's body from a well in Sanganai!",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Jaffna. The dead body of an elderly woman has been recovered from a well in Arali Road, Sanganai area under Manipai Police Division.",
        "Preliminary investigations by the police revealed that the woman was suffering from neurotic disorder and told her relatives that \"I don't want to trouble you\".",
        "An elderly woman named Kanthiya Annamma (81 years old) from Sanganai area has been recovered as a dead body. In this case, Manipai police are conducting further investigations regarding the incident."
      ],
